novému študentovi, moja krv sa začne búriť.

85
00:06:09,700 --> 00:06:11,620
A nakoniec, krvácam z nosa...

86
00:06:12,580 --> 00:06:13,990
Krvácanie z nosa...

87
00:06:13,990 --> 00:06:15,790
Keď sa priblížiš?

88
00:06:15,790 --> 00:06:16,500
Tvoja krv?

89
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:18,580
