134
00:09:02,250 --> 00:09:03,910
Prestaň robiť také veci!

135
00:09:05,170 --> 00:09:06,380
Také veci?

136
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:08,790
Povedal som, že som ťa videl, nie?

137
00:09:08,790 --> 00:09:10,300
V deň, keď som prestúpil.

138
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:11,090
V parku.

139
00:09:13,010 --> 00:09:14,340
T-To bolo...

140
00:09:14,340 --> 00:09:16,430
Neviem, aké úmysli si mala s ním...

141
00:09:16,430 --> 00:09:18,680
ale muchlovať sa s mužom v strednom veku...

142
00:09:19,510 --> 00:09:22,770
On by sa muchloval s hocijakým dievčaťom z "výšky", že?

143
00:09:22,770 --> 00:09:25,310
Ak sa bojíš, že by sa to stalo, prestaň s tým!

144
00:09:25,310 --> 00:09:28,150
Muž v strednom veku a dievča z "výšky"?

145
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:35,450
N-Nič také sme nerobili!

146
00:09:35,780 --> 00:09:37,740
Tak prečo hovoríš tak divne.

147
00:09:37,740 --> 00:09:39,910
Hovorím, že to nie je tak!

148
00:09:39,910 --> 00:09:40,700
Nie je?

149
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:47,000
<I>Takže nemá tušenie, že som ho pohrýzla.</I>.

150
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:50,750
<I>Teraz si myslí niečo iné!</I>

151
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:54,510
<I>Ale pravdu mu povedať nemôžem.</I>.

152
00:09:54,970 --> 00:09:56,970
<I>Č-Čo mám urobiť?</I>

153
00:09:58,680 --> 00:09:59,220
Hej.

154
00:10:01,060 --> 00:10:02,060
Karin.

155
00:10:02,060 --> 00:10:03,270
Onii-chan!
(Starší brat)

156
00:10:03,270 --> 00:10:04,930
Počkaj, kto je to dievča?

157
00:10:04,930 --> 00:10:07,480
Neboj sa, to je moja malá sestrička.

158
00:10:08,850 --> 00:10:11,110
Mimochodom, ideš už domov?

159
00:10:11,110 --> 00:10:12,820
Cítim sa sama.

160
00:10:13,820 --> 00:10:15,610
Aj ja sa cítim sám.

161
00:10:20,030 --> 00:10:22,660
Priletím za tebou čo najskôr.

162
00:10:22,660 --> 00:10:26,660
Sme ako rozdielne póly magnetu,
ktoré sa od seba neoddelia.

163
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,040
Ren...

164
00:10:31,590 --> 00:10:32,670
Tešilo ma...

165
00:10:33,210 --> 00:10:34,630
